name: HIFI
description: HiFi is the GameFi P2E platform integrating DeFi and Metaverse earning users HIFI daily to play games. Building multiple properties including HiFi Gaming (Platform), HiFi TV (entertainment for gaming, NFTs, Music), and Metaverse Journeys (Role Playing NFTs). HIFI’s mission is to create pathways for gamers/artists to build a career and lifestyle on the blockchain. Simultaneously, we’re attracting gaming developers/studios to list games and reactivate revenue utilizing HIFI’s reward engine.
